Package ours.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Schedule
    The Schedule interface defines all of the methods that a Schedule will require.
    User
    The User interface defines all of the required methods for a User of the Online University Registration System (OURS).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    The Course Class is used to hold all of the necessary data for a Course at the University
    DepartmentSchedule
    The DepartmentSchedule Class is the Schedule for an Academic Department at the University.
    Instructor
    The Instructor Class contains all of the information for an Instructor at the University.
    InstructorSchedule
    The InstructorSchedule class is the Schedule class for an Instructor at the University.
    Login
    The Login Class is used by the User to access their respective system.
    MasterSchedule
    The MasterSchedule class is the Schedule for the entire University.
    Read
    The Read Class is used to read files that the other classes require.
    Staff
    The Staff class contains all of the relevant information about a member of an Academic Department's Administrative Staff.
    Student
    The Student class contains all of the relevant information for a Student at the University.
    StudentSchedule
    The StudentSchedule class is the Schedule for a Student of the University.
    Write
    The Write class is used to write information to files that are required by the other classes.
